Package uk.ac.ebi.masscascade.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Chromatogram
    This is a chromatogram that describes a chromatographic profile.
    Index
    This is an index enumerating all available task classes that can run within the callable framework.
    Option
    This is an option describing required methods for a valid task option.
    Profile
    This is a profile that is comprised of data points defining time, m/z, and intensity values.
    Property
    This is a property that characterises objects.
    Range
    This is a range defined by a lower and upper bound.
    RunManager
    This is a random access file manager.
    Scan
    This is a scan that is comprised of m/z-intensity data points.
    Spectrum
    This is a spectrum that is comprised of a list of profiles.
    Task
    Top-most interface that is implemented by all task classes that are callable.
    Trace
    This is a mass chromatographic trace.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CallableTask
    An abstract implementation of a callable task class.
